# 🛡️ Design Document

## Secure Role-Based Task & Collaboration System

---

# 📌 1. Introduction

The **Secure Role-Based Task & Collaboration System** is a full-stack web application designed to manage tasks efficiently within a team environment. It ensures secure access using authentication and role-based authorization while providing a modern dashboard for tracking progress.

---

# 🎯 2. Objective

* To build a secure task management system
* To implement role-based access control
* To provide a user-friendly dashboard for tracking tasks
* To enable collaboration between admin and users

---

# 👥 3. Users & Roles

| Role  | Description                                  |
| ----- | -------------------------------------------- |
| ADMIN | Creates, assigns, updates, and deletes tasks |
| USER  | Views assigned tasks and updates status      |

---

# 🧩 4. System Overview

The system consists of two main components:

* **Frontend (React)** → User Interface
* **Backend (Spring Boot)** → Business Logic & Security

---

# 🏗️ 5. System Architecture

```id="6j1e2p"
Frontend (React)
       ↓
REST APIs (Axios)
       ↓
Spring Boot Backend
       ↓
Service Layer
       ↓
Repository Layer (JPA)
       ↓
Database (MySQL)
```

---

# 🛠️ 6. Technology Stack

## Frontend

* React.js
* Axios
* React Router
* CSS
* React Icons

## Backend

* Spring Boot
* Spring Security
* JWT Authentication
* Hibernate (JPA)
* MySQL / H2

---

# 📁 7. Module Design

## 🔐 Authentication Module

* Login using email and password
* JWT token generation
* Token validation for API access

---

## 👤 User Module

* Stores user details (email, password, role)
* Role-based access control

---

## 📋 Task Module

* Create tasks
* Assign tasks to users
* Update task status
* Delete tasks

---

## 📊 Dashboard Module

* Displays task statistics
* Shows tasks in Kanban board format
* Groups tasks by status

---

## 🔍 Search Module

* Live search filtering
* Search based on title and description

---

## 🔔 Notification Module

* Displays count of pending tasks
* Updates dynamically

---

# 🧠 8. Database Design

## User Table

| Field    | Type   |
| -------- | ------ |
| id       | Long   |
| email    | String |
| password | String |
| role     | String |

---

## Task Table

| Field         | Type   |
| ------------- | ------ |
| id            | Long   |
| title         | String |
| description   | String |
| status        | String |
| priority      | String |
| deadline      | Date   |
| assigned_user | String |

---

# 🔄 9. Workflow

1. User logs in
2. JWT token is generated
3. Token stored in localStorage
4. User requests tasks
5. Backend validates token
6. Tasks are returned based on assigned user
7. User updates task status
8. Dashboard updates dynamically

